String-Compare-Length 
==================================

With this module, you can calculate the difference in 
length between a string and the average length of strings 
in an array. Not limiting itself to simple arrays, the 
module also accomodates hashes of arrays. You can also 
compare the average lengths of strings in two arrays.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

None

